  <title>Texas - 2020 Census - Counties</title>
  <abstract>2020 Census, Counties in Texas. A "key" field has been added so data formatted or published by the council can be joined to the shapefile. Additional fields support labeling and cartography in Texas Legislative Council applications.

Texas extract of Counties from the Census Bureau's 2020 Census Redistricting Data (P.L. 94-171) TIGER/Line® shapefile. All legal boundaries and names are as of January 1, 2020. The boundaries shown are for Census Bureau statistical data collection and tabulation purposes only. This digital geographic data is used in the RedAppl and DistrictViewer redistricting applications, and other Texas Legislative Council mapping and reporting applications.</abstract>
